{"tid":731511,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"透過 HKG 分享一則貼文：【港姐2018】香港小姐首輪面試直撃　候選佳麗邊個會入圍","createTime":"2018-07-06T08:42:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T08:43:48.000Z","uid":14191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b67a3c08fa8caba750a420b1e64953c5bd905939","tid":731511,"uid":14191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T08:42:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2105000/2109343/miss_HK_thumb_20180706_J_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2105000%2F2109343%2Fmiss_HK_thumb_20180706_J_1024.jpg&h=57a9e45f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n年度選美盛事《2018香港小姐競選》在今天（7月6日）於將軍澳電視城進行首輪面試。當中參加香港小姐面試者燕瘦橫肥，水平不免參差。TOPick在電視城直擊報導面試首輪面試情況，並不斷更新，你覺得哪位最有冠軍相？<br />\r\n<br />\r\n【12：50】大會表示，今年香港小姐競選約有200人報名。其中參加者有已是藝人或有參加選美經驗，比如前女團as one成員Nata、參加過ViuTV《美選D.N.A.》的湯沛宜。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n【13：25】19歲北京舞蹈學院3年級生姚羽嘉，有意來香港發展。她表現因為最近演舞台劇要增肥，所以比較豐滿。她有信心入圍及希望奪冠。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2105000/2109343/MISSHK2018_0000_1024.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2105000%2F2109343%2FMISSHK2018_0000_1024.JPG&h=52a58ab6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n姚羽嘉。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2105000/2109343/MISSHK2018_0001_1024.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2105000%2F2109343%2FMISSHK2018_0001_1024.JPG&h=8f335333&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n【13：33】23歲水教練Honey Ho，身材很fit，對今次面試表示：「OK有信心」。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2105000/2109343/MISSHK2018_0046_1024.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2105000%2F2109343%2FMISSHK2018_0046_1024.JPG&h=ebecda70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n【13：40】打扮略成熟的Sonia，不來只18歲並在今天生日。她由媽媽陪同面試，其母親表示想女兒見下世面。"},{"pid":"c0fe8947e10928b2c962bd3fca2a62a8867ddeb4","tid":731511,"uid":14191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T08:43:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主做乜鳩<br />\n個標題想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返去搵牙joe啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}